    <section id = "aboutthecity">
        <h2>About The City</h2>
        <p>The Endless city began growing in 1754, when Jacque le Bouffon accidentally brought his house to life. Since then, the City has spread into and around other major urban centers, and incorporating</p>
        <p>them into its design. Not much more is known about its properties, other than the fact that Jacque remains the only one who could ever control it. Thankfully, we've found a way to tame The City,</p>
        <p>and prevent it from growing further.</p>
